The paper discusses Bayesian agents learning from private signals and the actions of others, which suggests a focus on game theory (cs.GT) and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). The concept of social learning also suggests a potential fit for social and information networks (cs.SI) and systems and control (cs.SY).
